{"tid":1412641,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"藍奕邦 - 六月","createTime":"2019-08-05T07:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T07:35:08.000Z","uid":277349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c30192ba8b2af38bc41243c2cc84acc8c4fb7982","tid":1412641,"uid":277349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:22:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hQpdqTl9HLg&amp;fbclid=IwAR2H4edHjQ3atW9Cyyprn9qMDz9zEyliLCt4EEBJv3YrP-nPdRGulGoHgdQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhQpdqTl9HLg%26fbclid%3DIwAR2H4edHjQ3atW9Cyyprn9qMDz9zEyliLCt4EEBJv3YrP-nPdRGulGoHgdQ&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWGa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=bd9b04cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hQpdqTl9HLg&amp;fbclid=IwAR2H4edHjQ3atW9Cyyprn9qMDz9zEyliLCt4EEBJv3YrP-nPdRGulGoHgdQ</a><br />\n<br />\n曲/詞: 藍奕邦<br />\n編曲/監製: 藍奕邦/李漢金<br />\n<br />\n別 恨自己生於這悲情世代<br />\n怎麼永垂不朽 轉眼亦已不再<br />\n像 六月天空都會忽然飛霜<br />\n把它當 美景仔細慢嚐 <br />\n<br />\n慘 偏偏醉人漂亮 偏偏嘆為觀止<br />\n哀傷偏要是最博得俗世讚賞<br />\n淚光閃得明亮 亦可教人欣賞<br />\n勝過自彈自唱<br />\n<br />\n@我對天 高聲一再呼喊 從無回覆一下<br />\n也許它根本當凡人是個笑話<br />\n淚滴變成飛花 人們無需念掛<br />\n愛不到我就算吧<br />\n(抱不起我亦能抱著雪花)@<br />\n<br />\n難道你們都感到害怕<br />\n<br />\n想 天天笑容燦爛 可惜世情冷酷<br />\n當中喜與怒樂與哀未到我揀<br />\n萬種悲歡離合 逐一化為灰燼<br />\n連同白雪花遍地瀰漫<br />\n<br />\nRepeat @ with ( )<br />\n<br />\n我也想 今生不再哭泣 樣樣事都不怕 <br />\n也許先要把最殘酷視作笑話<br />\n淚滴變成飛花 人們無需驚訝<br />\n再多悲壯亦能笑一笑吧<br />\n唯願我從此不再害怕"},{"pid":"d520a8fc80badf86547ecb1976ade40a5a752681","tid":1412641,"uid":204045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:35:08.000Z","msg":"推良心明星"}]}